snippet.title: ArcGIS for Server Architecture Explained
snippet.description:
Skip to 4:10 to jump to the ArcGIS Server Architecture piece. The first 4 minutes we discuss how to integrate ArcGIS server with Docker.

Full ArcGIS Server Playlist https://goo.gl/nkfM6Q

No docker in this episode because we need to explain the ArcGIS Server architecture in order to move forward. We talk about web servers (web adaptors) GIS Servers, config stores and how each component play a role in the ArcGIS server architecture
